articles.title: Americans are freed from Iran. So, why is the prisoner swap controversial for Biden? - USA TODAY
articles.description: The prisoner exchange could pave the way for better relations with Iran. But it has put President Joe Biden at further odds with Republicans.
articles.content:
WASHINGTON President Joe Biden is facing heat over his decision to go through with a controversial prisoner exchange between the U.S. and Iran.
